channel.title: Starting new account!
channel.description: Well I found an old botting account! Only has 294k on it but that's good enough. :D So I'm asking what kind off account should I make? I don't really want to start another main, so I'll be going with some kind of pure is thing, something melee/magic based and it doesnt matter if the account has to be members, I can get that anyway. So what kind of account should I make? I'm thinking some kind of pjer (I don't care what you think) but it's a great way to make money! I can play a few hours a day so I'm looking to get it completed in 3 months [b]!MAX![/b] So please do post on what type of account, why and about how long it would take! (remember it has to be something that can jump in fast and kill them before they notice!)
